Collamer, Respondent, v. Farrington, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 25, 1891.) Action by Warren' B. Collamer against Albert H. Farrington.

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Mayham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion to go to court of appeals denied. For opinion on appeal, see 15 N. Y. Supp. 452.
